data.description: Professional Pictures Coming Soon!  STOP!!! No need to look any further this home features 2 bedrooms, 2 bathroom and an office that can be easily converted into a bedroom. Also a swimming pool to cool you down in the hot summer months. A nice size shed on your oversized back yard enough room to entertain family and friends. This property has a lot of potential owner started a lot of projects that needs to be completed and with the right mindset this home can be a first timer's dream home or an investors great rental property. This home is being sold AS-IS.
